---
import Section from '../ui/Section.astro';
import FanoPlane from '../diagrams/FanoPlane.astro';
---

<Section id="hero" class="pt-32">
  <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-[3fr_2fr] gap-8 sm:gap-12 items-center" data-animate="hero">
    <div>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-glyph tracking-wide leading-tight" data-hero-headline>
        A self-organizing memory that replaces gradient descent with octonionic algebra
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-chalk max-w-xl" data-hero-paragraph>
        The octonionic trie is a tree whose nodes are individual octonions. It routes, stores, verifies, and restructures using five operations that emerge from a single algebraic substrate.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center sm:justify-end" data-hero-fano>
      <FanoPlane class="w-full max-w-[280px] sm:max-w-[400px]" />
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
